Class BCFKSLoadStoreParameter

java.lang.Object
com.distrimind.bouncycastle.jcajce.BCLoadStoreParameter
com.distrimind.bouncycastle.jcajce.BCFKSLoadStoreParameter
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.security.KeyStore.LoadStoreParameter
public class BCFKSLoadStoreParameter
extends BCLoadStoreParameter
LoadStoreParameter to allow configuring of the PBKDF used to generate encryption keys for use in the keystore.
